// ─── Phase-26 Slice 10: Cost-anomaly detector + escalation re-ranking ─
//
// Pure helpers. When a slice attempt costs > `threshold` × the plan median,
// the NEXT retry's escalation chain is re-ranked by `avg_cost_usd` ascending
